  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ allows users to attach special notes or instructions to any Purchase Orders and Inventory Transfers. Notes can include special formatting, embedded links, and images.</p><h3 id=\"PurchaseOrderNotes-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932787831/Purchase+Orders+List+View\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932787831\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Orders: List View</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932722231/Purchase+Order+Process+Creating+a+New+Purchase+Order\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932722231\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Order Process: Creating a New Purchase Order</a> </p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932427416/Purchase+Order+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932427416\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Order Resources</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"PurchaseOrderNotes-AddingNotestoPurchaseOrders(POs)\">Adding Notes to Purchase Orders (POs)</h2><p /><p>1. On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Inventory</strong> and create or view a purchase order/internal transfer.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: Inventory Transfers (Internal Purchase Orders) are available on Advanced and Professional plans.</p><p /><p>2. If viewing an existing Purchase Order, click the <strong>Edit button</strong> on the top right of the page to open the PO for editing.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. On the Purchase Order Edit screen, or when creating a new PO, click the <strong>Notes</strong> tab. Click inside the text field to enter your notes, links, or images. Once you are finished with your message, click <strong>Save Notes</strong>. If you are creating a new order, the note will be saved when the PO is Ordered.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"564\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: When attaching an image to a note, you will need to provide the source URL for the image. Our recommendation is to upload that image to an image-sharing website, then attach the linked URL to the note.</p><p /><p>4. After adding the note, you will be redirected Purchase Order View page. Scroll down and the note will appear under the Remarks section.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%205.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"PurchaseOrderNotes-EditingandDeletingNotesonPurchaseOrders\">Editing and Deleting Notes on Purchase Orders</h2><p>1. On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Inventory</strong> and view a purchase order/internal transfer.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%203.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. Click the <strong>Edit button</strong> on the top right of the page to open the PO for editing.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. On the Purchase Order Edit screen, click the <strong>Notes</strong> tab. Click inside the text field to edit the existing note. If you would like to delete the note, delete all of the text in this field. Once you are finished with your message, click <strong>Save Notes</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>4. After adding the note, you will be redirected to the Purchase Order View page. Scroll down and the edited note will appear under the Remarks section. If you removed the note altogether, there will not be a Remarks section. Scrolling down a bit further will show the Change Log for the PO, and this section displays a history of changes made to the Purchase Order, including updates to the Notes/Remarks section.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932591172/PO%20Notes%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
